Title: Series: A Collection of Etchings after the Most Eminent Masters of the Dutch and Flemish Schools
Description: The Flight into Egypt; the Virgin and the Christ Child on donkey, led by Joseph; small plate; copy in same direction after Rembrandt. c.1782-1803 Etching
Curator's comments: For the original etching by Rembrandt see F,4.100. For comment on the series see 1861,0413.56.
